Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:07.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NHuh? Repairing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.35,0:00:11.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Repairing the robot? Stop doing things whenever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:15.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to?\NWell, I haven't seen anyone from NASA.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I own a bicycle shop.\NSo what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I repair flat tires for so many years..\Nno..no...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:24.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Repair flat tires? ah...ah!\NYou're noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:29.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, as long as I repair in the shop,\Nit will be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:32.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you.\NWhat about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:34.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a high school teacher.\NI am curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:36.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:39.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am curious how do you teach your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:41.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am really a teacher!\NWith that short hand of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:43.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:50.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Bicycle shop.\NHigh school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:54.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you a robot?\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:57.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a robot~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:00.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! As for you...\Nyou are a high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:03.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm a robot...\NWell, yes you are but..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:06.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to remember that you act as high school student in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:10.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's it! Yes!\NYou have a face of a high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:13.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:15.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not how high school girls sound
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:19.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be I am a high school girl~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:21.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget what you're doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:28.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I made this with a lot of effort
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:30.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You will eat this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:31.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:34.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhhh...ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:37.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,sigh~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:45.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa~~ High school girls alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:47.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Waah!! What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Q10 is a high school girl right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:53.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes..isnt it obvious?\NHow can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're even wearing a high school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:58.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I become if I remove my uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:02.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As for that…\NYou're a robot right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:05.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no one calls me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:09.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If that is the case, then what am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to go out first. This is a men's toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that.\NYou saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:23.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well this is given to me….\NNot that one..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto.\NQ10?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:30.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have seen a sort of machine under the skin of her broken arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a robot right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,≪ Right! right! ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:40.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as i thought. She really is.\NThat's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:44.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a secret?\NUh..you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:47.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I'm not going to tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:51.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, can you give Kyuto to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:54.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean give to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you say that. Besides, I don't own her ..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?\NI don't have anything to do with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:01.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you will give her to me right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Give her to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:10.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Young master pinch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:14.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,During this time, it's useless to pinch your mouth. You must have a poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:16.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She even has a poker face even if you don't tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:19.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nakao-kun can see right through you right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:23.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Nakao-kun can see right through you that far
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:26.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't hear you right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:29.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?\NBy the way, he has no other choice right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it will be his, he wont even tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:37.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, do you mean he will press the reset button?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:42.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Nakao-kun must press again the molar switch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in real life, there is no such thing as reset button
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For the adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,there are certain things that the eye cannot see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes there is.\NThere is. There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But...well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:57.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, I'm still wondering how did it happen\NSuch thing does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you mention it\NMaybe there is a back up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff.\NPuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:05.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there is no problem.\NSorry that I spent more time caring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But!\NThis round has been decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:12.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always have time to make things come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:15.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NDon't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:19.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not forcing myself!\NIt will be fine if she's with Nakao.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:27.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, no one can replace you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:32.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, just like a situation today which is happening slowly..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:37.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a harmless child and a cool bad person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:43.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Even if it wasn't me, that will be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your switch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:54.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to press it accidentaly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:57.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But Heita was the one who pressed it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:00.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I met Heita..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I am walking with you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:07.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'm going to lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like when the sun sets
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:22.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to see Kyuto's ugly uniform..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:27.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear the strange way of your talking
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:31.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where then can I hear your voice that sounds like a brass of a school band
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:48.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is a joke.\NJoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:52.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, when you play..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:06:01.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, everything that happened has given me a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:05.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'm going to lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting. Here is Yaki-udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?\NI asked a favor from a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is a trial product.\NPerfume?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:53.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is perfume for dogs.\NFor the dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:56.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, a herbivorous type of dog is increasing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For the dogs..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:00.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I recovered the original type of Hindu dog and returned it to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:04.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kainushi-san you know.\NHmmm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man it stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:14.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Why are running away from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's scared of you\NSensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:20.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks that you're a beast.\NI am a beast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Chiro-chan! Chiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:28.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Mou~~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:35.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a high school teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:41.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes you are..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiro-chan~~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:50.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a misunderstanding ~~\NHow can I be a beast? Jeezz
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiro-chan~! You found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:02.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I found her because of the beating of her heart.\NBeating of her heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:05.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Her heart beat is like one, two, one, two..Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can identify by using such thing.\NPuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:12.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome.\NNext time, tell me what sound it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:18.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fukai Heita's sound" What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,My sound??
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,≪ This is bad ≫\N≪ Self centered person≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,≪ So cool! ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:33.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the girl in the internet that is found out to have red eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? "Red eye"? It's not red hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:38.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wig! Wig!\NEh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((It seems that there is a fight happening in the internet))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((I've seen it. I've seen it. She's hanging out with dangerous people))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:50.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((I saw Takashi and midlle-aged man entering the Love Hotel))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((What kind of friends does she have))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:58.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((It seems that, that high school student has very bad character))\N((It's really worst!))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:04.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the manual?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:08.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There is none.\NNone?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:11.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can ask her anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh~oh~..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:17.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There is an outlet in her waist. You can try charge her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really really?~ Ehhh~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can charge her at least 17 hours in a day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:26.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there will come a time that she will suddenly turn off.\NSo, you have to carry her on your back when you go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry her on my back when going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you know what I know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the startup switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh..the switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The molar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The reset button is in the left molar.\NTake care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Molar?　You mean molar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:10:00.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean molar?\NWhy molar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:31.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have transferred Kyuto to Nakao right now.\NBussiness completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:35.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuu~ it seems that you can't do poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:42.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you don't want it if you really don't want it.\NI don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:44.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kyuto will be found out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,there will probably be a terrible thing going to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:49.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why if only I can hold it further,\Nthen it will be ok. But then I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way professor, you didn't think that I can do such thing right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:56.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well that's your opinion. I have also an opinion in my position
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:11:02.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I am standing somewhere else while you are standing in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:05.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for us to stand in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:09.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you standing firmly right now professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:15.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably in a place where truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:18.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A place where I can do everything for someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:21.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can do everything?\NYup
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Fukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:30.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NI can't reset her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:38.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry reset her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:12:01.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be fine wherever I stand right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:06.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is up to you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:23.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give Kyuto to you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:28.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised, right?\NI will say something about her on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will say that Fukai's lover is a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to reveal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:41.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious!　\NI'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:48.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?\NNakao is seriously going to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:52.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really an idiot.\NIt'll be ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:55.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not ok!\NRumors spreads so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There will come a day that everybody will stop talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody will think that I don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:06.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe its not perfect. I don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:12.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But Heita kun is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:24.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita-kun's sound.\NMy sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:40.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the sound of Heita-kun's heart.\N[Earphone] (heart beat)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:46.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita-kun is here\N[Earphone] (beat)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:51.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever sound it is.\NHeita is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:06.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is~\NJust as I thought. It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:11.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Inhaling with mere sleeping chill.\NWho do you think you are talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you're a doctor right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:17.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have read everything about Iryu manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:24.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lip has a good color.\NGood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok. Breathe please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:33.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... There's nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:36.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think there's nothing wrong?\NI said, it's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok. Let's listen at the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa~~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:47.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I got fascinated for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:50.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:53.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fascinated by it? No way..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:57.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back with a good back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:15:00.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:02.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:07.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take a picture of it?\NPicture?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:11.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...well sure you can,\NOk..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:18.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa~ This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:24.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's a back of a man right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:27.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey..Is it really true that Kageyama is going to Canada?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:30.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?\NWhere else? Nanpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop doing that in front of Kawai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?　What happened?\NIt's too terrible. Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:44.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really terrible.\NWhat are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That you're going to Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're going
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:56.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok wherever you go. But it would be better if you have told me 1 week ahead of time.  I don't have a problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:16:00.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you should have asked me first..\NIt could be longer than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Longer than 1 week?\NWell, therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That high school that I have told you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:10.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,An acquaintance from work helped me apply to working in videos
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:15.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What about college? Let's go together...\NAbout that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:24.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I really want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:31.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back to a place wherein you are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:39.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, I have no expectations nor hope. And I was fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:44.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I won't get hurt forever
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:48.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wary, but still I wanted to live
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:53.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I am being punished?\NMaybe because of my ugly voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:56.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think of that? You are not ugly at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:17:00.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to break up with me right?\NWhat are you talking about? I don't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:03.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mad.\NI'm not mad.\NYou're angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:10.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're thinking that I am troublesome.\NYou're thinking like that right?\NI'm not thinking of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like poker face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:27.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\NIt is cute if you keep doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:31.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I cannot make anyone lively right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:36.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to uplift someone spirit?\NPuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:41.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always say "puff"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be able to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:49.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be able to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:56.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you bothered Heita?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:02.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,During this time, let's get depressed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:05.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,With a robot….?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:11.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto is depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:22.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I not depressed enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Gan~~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Gan~~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:45.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your spirit came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:49.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yea~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:51.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:03.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if we could go together
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:15.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Far away from here forever
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:39.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:42.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:47.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When you open that, something terrible happens
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:53.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The power is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:58.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it will be ours, we want to do something out from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:05.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that someone with power can do everything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:09.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,to the world right now which is broken
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:13.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to break it right?\NThe world right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:16.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Our world right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:19.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To really break the so called great world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:23.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Never\NDo not break a world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:31.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are person who cannot make it happen.If you cannot get hold of great power
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:37.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really want it.\NI'm telling you I really want a hell of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:39.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:44.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am, just like you, wanted to have more great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:46.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the telephone\NWrite it in the internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:48.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you tell someone about it.\NThey will not believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:50.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just telling you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:55.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:10.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((Red eye, she's happy right?))\N((I have seen that red haired girl))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:12.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((It's not red))\N((That is a wig))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:16.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((Lie ~ I'm ignoring everyone))\N((Is that true. I'm really pissed off))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:20.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((What?　She must be living well as high school.))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:27.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:36.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you perhaps that one?\NThe one abused in the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:39.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing such things without asking permission
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will eventually get tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:48.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the only one telling me this face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:52.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody knows it. Nobody tells me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:55.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no voice that will come out to say..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:58.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's not true"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:05.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will always say I'm not lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:12.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where will I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:15.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They might think that "there is no such human being.."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:18.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"that is able to face someone by being like that" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:21.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to laugh out loud!\NI want to shout out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:23.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:27.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't reach it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:30.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Me who has no name..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:34.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And has no face to look at them.\NHow am I able to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:37.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:45.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say "I'm not like that!" in a song right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:48.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use it by knocking the rumors one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:52.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let me hear you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:57.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our band.\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:03.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you can listen to it, I'm going to give it to you.\NReally? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:07.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so good.\NYou're giving me something that you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:15.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I dyed my hair red?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:18.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm..because it's cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:22.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it. It's because I'll stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:25.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei advised it..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:29.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone looked at me, surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:34.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then at that time, I was able to think that "I am here"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:37.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then rock after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.54,0:23:40.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:43.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:48.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, you have a partner right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:54.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean partner? I am a stand up comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:03.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?\NThat is something to cover the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.05,0:24:07.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?　Is this the latest trend?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.06,0:24:12.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for?\NHmmm..medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.63,0:24:15.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine??
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:19.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Is this the one?\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.55,0:24:24.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.54,0:24:29.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see you angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.58,0:24:33.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.02,0:24:42.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I have a question..\NHmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.02,0:24:45.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a time that you lose your patience?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.03,0:24:49.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there is..there is.\NLike this foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.05,0:24:51.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.01,0:24:54.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A, keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.05,0:25:00.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we want to have it. Living is a proof that we have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.02,0:25:03.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, during that time when you were hospitalized,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.53,0:25:06.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you don't want anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.53,0:25:09.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But then suddenly, you said, "I want to eat tomato"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.53,0:25:12.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there is some guy who bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.54,0:25:17.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The aisle that sells vegetables look lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.09,0:25:19.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, the supermarket looks the same as usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.53,0:25:23.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "I still want it.."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.03,0:25:25.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.52,0:25:29.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you want to listen to a tale of death
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.04,0:25:32.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you really want to hear is "I have a long way to live"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.06,0:25:38.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.38,0:26:00.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiro-chan~~!\NChiro-chan~! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.05,0:26:02.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You still able to smell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.56,0:26:05.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! It's me you know! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.56,0:26:10.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back Chiro-chan~!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.56,0:26:15.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to present an incredible invention you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.07,0:26:20.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada! "All about poverty"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.07,0:26:23.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When I paste whatever expensive in here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:26.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It will instantly look poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.55,0:26:29.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.06,0:26:59.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Next...Where will I paste the rest~~?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.13,0:27:02.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.08,0:27:05.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you afraid of poverty?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.05,0:27:10.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, as for poverty,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.06,0:27:13.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think if you see something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.56,0:27:19.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For Fujioka-kun, this is just a lot of paper that I keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.15,0:27:23.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like that.\NIf you really care for it, it will grow like Hagasen right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.57,0:27:31.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.\NAs long as it is pasted thoroughly, It'll be completely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.56,0:27:36.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.57,0:27:45.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.56,0:27:54.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me Kyuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.08,0:27:57.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second...\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.07,0:28:00.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.14,0:28:01.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I am begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.06,0:28:10.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.07,0:28:14.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She is not a thing.\NFor me, Kyuto is...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.07,0:28:19.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,someone that I can't give to anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.08,0:28:22.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I can't give her up
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.15,0:28:28.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that for Nakao, Kyuto is..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.07,0:28:31.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,a thing that you have to own...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.56,0:28:36.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to think that way
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.58,0:28:39.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto is a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:54.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to her to me,\NI am going to jump from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.00,0:28:57.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...\NI'm going to ask you..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.01,0:29:01.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Between human life and robot, who do you think is more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.00,0:29:05.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.51,0:29:17.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.99,0:29:20.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.54,0:29:33.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kyuto
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.50,0:29:39.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.52,0:29:41.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!　Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.02,0:29:45.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.01,0:30:10.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.53,0:30:14.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you must continue to live
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.58,0:30:17.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In my broken world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.02,0:30:21.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai Heita fell down. How are you going to face reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.51,0:30:27.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you have used force in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.49,0:30:42.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.49,0:31:13.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.51,0:31:16.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.51,0:31:30.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'm going to throw back Fukai Heita
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.01,0:31:32.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? No way..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.50,0:31:35.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-kun please catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.50,0:31:38.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute...\NThat's impossible! I'm telling you! That's absolutely impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.02,0:31:39.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.55,0:31:41.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.07,0:31:42.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.00,0:31:51.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.00,0:32:12.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.52,0:32:15.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!　Chiro-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.52,0:32:20.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back~~\NYosh..yosh. You really came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.03,0:32:24.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? A!\NYou came back because of my smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.01,0:32:26.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Yosh..yosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.05,0:32:28.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.60,0:32:32.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that I was not of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.02,0:32:36.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, I still love you\NI will give anything you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.53,0:32:40.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in order to become someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.51,0:32:45.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do it my way\NI want to move forward..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.02,0:32:47.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.55,0:32:51.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to a place far away for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.51,0:32:54.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well..no..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.53,0:32:58.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I am going to get that cue..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.04,0:33:09.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.08,0:33:12.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.03,0:33:18.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai almost died because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.48,0:33:22.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe I was really about to die
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.00,0:33:25.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whichever it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.01,0:33:27.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.02,0:33:39.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the room
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.02,0:33:41.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,where I found Kyuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.51,0:33:48.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't entered the switch yet and\Nshe was sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.55,0:33:55.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happen to found her first
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.99,0:34:00.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I understand what you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.01,0:34:04.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's unfair right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.51,0:34:09.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like unfairness right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.52,0:34:14.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,“Why is it only me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.59,0:34:18.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Within me, I am resenting like an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.50,0:34:24.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you thinking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.50,0:34:26.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.50,0:34:30.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well that…disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.49,0:34:36.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your fault. Still you have a lot of resentment?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.08,0:34:38.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.52,0:34:45.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I have resentment, there's nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.02,0:34:48.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.49,0:34:54.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore “the world's unfairness" is a good thing..
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.01,0:34:56.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.00,0:35:03.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.02,0:35:06.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not only me that saw all this
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.99,0:35:10.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.51,0:35:15.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Being resentful or being jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.52,0:35:24.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even those rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.49,0:35:28.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little they are collapsing. That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.51,0:35:32.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But as for small things, I know
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.50,0:35:34.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That it will still be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.99,0:35:40.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will surely think of it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.52,0:35:50.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.50,0:35:54.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.06,0:35:56.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.02,0:36:06.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, here is the CD set.\NHmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.50,0:36:09.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,New song of Ohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.02,0:36:11.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, it's not yet done?\NIt's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.51,0:36:13.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.53,0:36:17.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!　Mom, it's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.55,0:36:22.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go. Yosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.50,0:36:28.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? That's a performace?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.52,0:36:32.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. This is a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.51,0:36:35.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.00,0:36:37.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fukai Heita's sound"?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.09,0:36:45.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound of Heita's heart beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.51,0:36:49.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.01,0:36:52.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.02,0:36:56.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.00,0:36:59.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sincerely moving properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.04,0:37:03.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So this is the sound of Heita
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.00,0:37:33.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ I am here
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.51,0:37:39.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ I am crying hard enough
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.08,0:37:51.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ I am crying hard enough
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.49,0:37:55.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to tell a story although it can't be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.49,0:37:59.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that it's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.52,0:38:04.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You will write in a blackboard?\NBy the way, when I look back,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.49,0:38:08.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The classroom is empty.\NI think there are times that it's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.54,0:38:11.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the one who will act as villain or something
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.09,0:38:14.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no empty classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.01,0:38:16.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a metaphor, metaphor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.50,0:38:19.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For example! Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.50,0:38:23.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no empty classrooms
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.01,0:38:24.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.00,0:39:24.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you decide to take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.50,0:39:28.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a high school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.00,0:39:30.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What came up to you suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.51,0:39:33.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am a high school teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.03,0:39:36.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that everytime I see your back.\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.56,0:39:38.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.53,0:39:55.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((Between human life and robot, which do you think is more important?))
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.01,0:39:57.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((Kyuto))
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.57,0:40:03.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even small things that fell have
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.02,0:40:06.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,entered to a small opening
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.53,0:40:09.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.50,0:40:12.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even nonexistent thing such as myself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.50,0:40:16.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,will become bigger to the extent that I won't be able to manage it...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.52,0:40:20.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was uneasy last night. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.09,0:40:24.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You have always felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.99,0:40:28.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the night before your surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.51,0:40:32.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That night when a patient died in the same room
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.00,0:40:35.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That night when you were waiting for the test results
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.00,0:40:38.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.01,0:40:41.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry..I have forgotten all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.10,0:40:49.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...You were happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.02,0:40:53.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You are happy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.99,0:40:59.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...\NSo there is a day that you have forgotten all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.56,0:41:06.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the place for you already
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.50,0:41:14.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the place for me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.01,0:41:16.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to decide a place for your own
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.50,0:41:20.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((That is for you to decide))
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.50,0:41:24.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really decide it for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.02,0:41:26.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.07,0:41:29.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, even to a dangerous place?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.99,0:41:33.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice if that place is really meant for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.00,0:41:36.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the best place for you. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.52,0:41:45.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.49,0:41:52.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That tower it is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.50,0:41:57.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto said that "a world is born"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.00,0:41:59.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is that tower
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.49,0:42:07.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that wherever place is ok as long as I am with Kyuto
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.58,0:42:10.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is that tower
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.00,0:42:16.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If my place is that tower
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.02,0:42:18.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is probably also Kubo's place
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.51,0:42:22.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there is Kageyama's place
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.00,0:42:27.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That one is Yamamoto's place
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.53,0:42:30.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Fujioka's place
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.60,0:42:33.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao's place
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.01,0:42:35.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai's place
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.52,0:42:41.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We are all standing facing towards the same sky
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.51,0:42:45.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As we are all facing towards the sky screaming
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.00,0:42:48.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,no voice is coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.54,0:42:54.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand the meaning of feeling good sinking deeply down the root
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.51,0:42:59.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As I extend my hand mutually,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.01,0:43:03.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We are connected only by an unreliable electric wire..
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.52,0:43:07.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.54,0:43:13.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am standing on this ground trying hard
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.51,0:43:19.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am right here. Standing right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.53,0:43:30.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaa...that's right..
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.12,0:43:40.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We are all here
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.51,0:45:16.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This drama theme song is "Honto no Kimochi" by Takahashi Yu CD
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.05,0:45:18.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We will give presents to those first 100 people who buy this CD
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.60,0:45:21.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send your postcards to the address shown below
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.01,0:45:22.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We are looking forward to it
